creator: PSYNET
descriptionHtml:
*** Good people SNS ***

‘Hi there’ is an SNS application in which you can share the memory of moments through talk, location, blog and make various friends. Enjoy stories and lives with more than 3500000 ‘Hi there’ members.

By the tag, make diverse off-line communities with the ‘Hi there’ members who have the same interests with you Also, share ‘Hi there’ including your own daily life, with the members.

The attractive ‘Hi there’ members cause cheerful and vigorous events.

The members who uploads the ‘Talks full of information, impression and fun’ are sometimes are introduced to many other people.

Attach your alarm to your friends! Then you will recognize news from your mate and a real-time talk. Have a Talk more by comments!

Actually, some impressive couples got married through ‘Hi there’.

Build a house on the ‘Hi there” map. Then Look for another ‘Hi there’ member in the same area and get along with them!
